description: Fetta Di Casa means “Slice of Home” in Italian, and with the warm, friendly service you find at this family-run truck, alongside their scrumptious artisanal Neapolitan-style pizzas, you are sure to feel right at home with every bite. This talented crew stays absolutely true to Italian tradition, by only using the finest locally sourced ingredients to make these hand rolled pizzas, like Broccoli & Feta, Twice Baked Potato, BBQ Chicken, Pineapple & Bacon, just to list a few of the toppings you can choose. You can even enjoy all this great pizza without the wait, with their custom-built Earthstone oven, firing at 900 degrees, each pizza is baked to perfection in just 2-3 minutes. Eat at Fetta Di Casa and you too will agree that “Everything is Betta with Fetta!”
name: Fetta Di Casa
